\id JAS Meitei: Roman Script 1st Translation 
\h Jacob 
\toc1 JACOB-NA I-ba Chithi 
\toc2 Jacob 
\toc3 Jac 
\mt1 JACOB-NA 
\mt2 I-ba Chithi 
\imt1 Wahoudok 
\ip Jacob hairiba lairik asi Jacob kouba mioi amana ibani. Anganba matamgi singlupki luchingba ama oiba amasung Jerusalem-gi ahanlupki maraktasu yaoba (Pakhonchatpa 15:13) Jisugi manaonupa Jacob haiba mahak asi oiramba yai. Mahakpu Galatia singlupki yumbini haina Pakhonchatpa Paul-nasu hairammi. (Galatians 2:9). Akhang-aheisinggi matung inna Jacob hairiba lairik asi chourakna Christta poklaba matung chahi 50 mukki matungda iramgani haina thajanei. Jacob asi Jerusalem-gi ahal amagi pham paiba maramna lairik asi Jerusalem-da leiringeida iramba yai. 
\ip Lairik asi ‚ÄúPhurup kayagi marakta chaikhaiduna leiba Jihudigi salai taretta‚Äù¬î i-ba lairikni (Jacob 1:1). Masida yaoriba parasing asi Christian pumnamakna sijinnaba yaba ngaktani adubu mapham asida ‚Äúsalai taret‚Äù¬î haiba wahei asi yaoba maramna Jihudi Christian-singda i-ba oigani haiba adu utli. Masida hiram kaya yaoba maramna, lairik asi mioi kangbu kayada younaba ibani haiba khang-i. Thajaba amadi thabak ani asigi marakta leinaba marida Jacob-na pukning chingsilli. Achumba thajaba adudi thabakna utkani (2:17). Inak-khunba misingda michang-mikhai naiba sajat chattanaba mahakna cheksin wa hairi (2:1-4) amasung eikhoina ngangba wasu cheksinnaba eikhoida haibiri (3:1-12). 
\iot Yaopham Takpa 
\io1 1. Jacob-na lairik asibu paribasingda khurumjaba \ior (1:1)\ior* 
\io1 2. Christian-singna awabada taba matamda khaangheinaba mahakna pukning thougatpa \ior (1:2-27)\ior* 
\io1 3. Thajababu thabakna utpa haibasi kayada mathou tabano haibadu mahakna haiba \ior (2:1-26)\ior* 
\io1 4. Madugi matungda wahei haibasi kayada panggal leibano haibadu mahakna haiba \ior (3:1-12)\ior* 
\io1 5. Tengban Mapugi oiba lousing aduga taibangpanbagi oiba lousing adugagi khennaba adu Jacob-na sandokna takpa \ior (3:13‚Äì4:10)\ior* 
\io1 6. Mathangda napal toubagi maiyokta Jacob-na cheksin wa haiba \ior (4:11‚Äì5:6)\ior* 
\io1 7. Mayamgi oiba paotak khara piraga Jacob-na lairik asi loisilli \ior (5:7-20)\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Mat 13:55; Mrk 6:3; Pakhon 15:13; Gal 1:19\x*Tengban Mapu amasung Mapu Ibungo Jisu Christtagi minai ama oiriba Jacob eihakna, 
\p Taibangpan-gi mapham pumnamakta ichai chaina leiriba Tengban Mapugi mi pumnamakta khurumjari. 
\s1 Thajaba amasung lousing 
\p  
\v 2 Eigi ichil inaosa, makhal makha kayagi changyengba nakhoida lakpa matamda nasamak laibak phabani haina singthanou  
\v 3 maramdi nakhoigi thajaba adu changyengba aduna khaangheiba thok-halli haiba nakhoina khang-i.  
\v 4 Nakhoida kari amata awatpa leitana, changkhonba amasung mapung phaba oinaba, khaangheiba adugi thabak mapung phahallu.  
\v 5 Adubu nakhoigi naraktagi kanagumbana lousing watlabadi, mi pumnamakta maral thibidana pinaheiba Tengban Mapugi maphamda mahakna haijasanu aduga madu mangonda pibigani.  
\v 6 Adubu mahakna haijaba matamda chingnaba leitana amadi thajana haijagadabani maramdi chingnaba mahak adudi nungsitna humdok humjin touduna puriba ipakki ithat-ipomgumbani.  
\v 7 Adugumba mioi aduna Mapu Ibungogi maphamdagi karigumba ama phanggani haina khandasanu.  
\v 8 Adugumba mioi adudi pukning ani longba amadi mahakna touba pumnamakta pukchel leptaba mini. 
\s1 Lairaba amadi inakkhunba 
\p  
\v 9 Lairaba thajabasing makhoibu Tengban Mapuna thanggatpiba matamda makhoina haraojasanu,  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Isa 40:6,7\x*aduga inakkhunba makhoi adu Tengban Mapuna nemthahanba matamda makhoina haraojasanu. Maramdi inakkhunba makhoi adu lamlakki leirangumna mangkhigani.  
\v 11 Numitna akanba meisaga loinna thoklak-i amasung pambi adu kanghalli aduga mapan adu kelli amasung madugi phajaba saktam adu mangkhi. Matou adugumna inakkhunba makhoi adusu makhoigi lallon-itik touna touna adum mangkhigani. 
\s1 Changyengba amadi athemba 
\p  
\v 12 Changyengba khaangliba mahak adu yaiphabani maramdi changyengba aduda mai paklaba mahak aduna, Tengban Mapuna mahakpu nungsiba misingda pibigani wasakpiba hingbagi luhup adu mahakna phangjagani.  
\v 13 Eikhoibu changyengbana themba matamda, ‚ÄúAthemba asi Tengban Mapudagi lakpani‚Äù¬î haina eikhoina khak hairoidabani. Maramdi Tengban Mapubu phattabana themba ngamde, amasung Ibungo mahakna kana amatabu themba toude.  
\v 14 Adubu eikhoi isagi phattaba apambasingna eikhoibu chingthoktuna langda thuhallabada eikhoibu themmi.  
\v 15 Adudagi eikhoigi phattaba apambasing aduna mirollabada pap pok-i, aduga pap aduna mapung pharabada siba pok-i. 
\p  
\v 16 Eigi nungsiraba ichil-inaosa, nakhoibu minamhan-ganu.  
\v 17 Aphaba amadi mapungphaba khudon khudingmak swardagini, swargagi mangalsingbu sembiba Tengban Mapudagi lakpani, mahakti mamigumna hongba amadi leithokpa leite.  
\v 18 Ibungo mahak masamakki ningbagi matung inna achumba wahei adugi mapanna mahakna eikhoibu pokpire, madu mahakki khutsem pumnamakki marakta eikhoina ahanba mapham phangnabani. 
\s1 Taba amasung touba 
\p  
\v 19 Eigi nungsiraba ichil inaosa, masi ningsingbiyu! Mi khudingna tabada thuba, aduga ngangbada tappa amasung saobada tappa oigadabani.  
\v 20 Mioibagi asaobana Tengban Mapuna oihanningba aphabasingsing adu purakte.  
\v 21 Maram aduna amotpa amasung phattaba lamchat pumnamak thadok-u. Nakhoibu kanbiba ngamba, nakhoigi thamoinungda thakhraba wa adu nolukna lousillu. 
\p  
\v 22 Wahei adu icham-chamna tabata oiduna nasabu minamjahan-ganu, madugi mahutta hairiba adu thabak oina pangthok-u.  
\v 23 Nahakna wa adu taraga thabak oina pangthoktrabadi, nahakti mingselda mahakmakki maithong yengba mi amagumbani  
\v 24 aduga mahak masabu yenglaga, chatkhraga mahak yengbada kari malli haibadu khudakta kaothok-i.  
\v 25 Ningtamba piba mapung phaba wayel yathang aduda pukning changna tattana yengba kanagumba mi haibadi makhoina taraba adu kaodaduna thabak oina pangthokpasingda Tengban Mapuna makhoina toujaba khudingmakta yaiphabata oihanbigani. 
\p  
\v 26 Nakhoigi narakta kanagumba amana masa mathantabu laining chetpani haina singthanajabra? Karigumba nahakki narei adu nahakna khudum chandrabadi nahakki laining adu arembani aduga nasa nathantabu minamjabani.  
\v 27 Ipa Ibungo Tengban Mapuna singthanaba asengba amadi achumba laining adudi: mama mapa leijadrab angangsing amadi lukhrabisingbu awa anada yengsinbiba amadi taibangpan asina mot-han-gadaba adudagi tonganna leiba adubuni. 
\c 2  
\s1 Michang mikhai naiba thingba 
\p  
\v 1 Eigi ichil inaosa, eikhoigi Mapu Ibungo Jisu Christta, matik mangalgi Mapu Ibungobu thajaba mising oina, mapanthonggi mawong matou yenglaga nakhoina misingda lamchat chatpa khak touganu.  
\v 2 Nakhoigi tinaphamda sanagi khudop siba amadi phajaba phijet setpa inakkhunba nupa ama aduga amotpa phi setpa lairaba nupa ama changlakpa thoklabadi,  
\v 3 maduda nakhoina aphaba phi set chaba mi aduda henna ikai khumnaba uttuna mangonda asumna hairabadi, ‚ÄúAphaba phamphamlang asida phambiyu,‚Äù¬î aduga lairaba mi adudana, ‚ÄúNahakti aduda lepu,‚Äù¬î nattraga ‚ÄúEigi khongnetpham manak asida phammu‚Äù¬î haina hairabadi,  
\v 4 adu oirabadi nakhoi nasen-gi narakta misak mimai yengba amadi phattaba wakhalna wayenbasing oiba nattra? 
\p  
\v 5 Nungsiraba ichil inaosa, eina haibasi tabiyu! Taibangpangi mityengda lairabani haina singthanaba misingbu thajabada inakkhunnanaba amadi Ibungo mahakpu nungsibasingda pibigani wasakpikhiba Ningthou leibak adu phangnanaba Tengban Mapuna khandokpiba nattra?  
\v 6 Adubu nakhoinadi lairabasingbu ikai khumnabide! Nakhoibu neihatpiba adu inakkhunbasingna nattra? Nakhoibu namduna wayelsangda chingduna puba adu makhoina nattra?  
\v 7 Nakhoigi mapu oiriba mahakki aphaba minglen adubu thina ngangbasing adu makhoising asi nattra? 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Levi 19:18\x* Mapugi puyada yaoriba Ningthou leibakki wayel yathang haibadi, ‚ÄúNangna nanggi keirol leikaibu nasamakkumna nungsiyu,‚Äù¬î haiba adubu illabadi, nakhoina achumba adu tourabani.  
\v 9 Adubu nakhoina misingbu makhoigi mapanthonggi matung-inna misak mimai yenglabadi, nakhoi pap toubani, aduga nakhoina Wayel Yathang thugaiba ama oina wayel yathangna nakhoibu aranba tahalli.  
\v 10 Kanagumba amana Wayel Yathang apumba ngakle hairaga, amakhak ngaktrabadi, wayel yathang apumba thugaibagi maral leirabani.  
\v 11 Maramdi Ibungo mahakna haiba, ‚ÄúMigi nupi migi nupa ngangnaganu,‚Äù¬î asisu hai ‚ÄúNahakna mi hatkanu.‚Äù¬î Nahakna migi nupi migi nupa ngangnabagi thabak toudraga, nahakna mi hatlabadi, nahak Wayel Yathang thugaiba mi ama haibadu oire.  
\v 12 Eikhoibu ningtamhanbiba Wayel Yathang aduna wayen-gadaba misinggumna, nakhoina ngangsu ngang-u tousu tou.  
\v 13 Maramdi minungsi leitaba mahak adu Tengban Mapuna wayenba matamda minungsi utloi, Wayenbabudi minungsina ngammi. 
\s1 Thajaba amasung thabak 
\p  
\v 14 Eigi ichil inaosa, kanagumba mi amana mahakki thajaba lei hairaga, thabak yaodrabadi, maduda kari tongjaba leibage? Adugumba thajaba aduna makhoibu kanbiba ngamgadra?  
\v 15 Kanagumba nachin nanao nattraga nachan nache ama setnaba phi amadi nongmagi channaba chara leitrabada,  
\v 16 nakhoi kanagumba amana makhoida asumna haibada, ‚ÄúTengban Mapuna nakhoida yaipha thoujal pibiba oisanu! Lumna leiyu, ningthina cha-thakpiyu!‚Äù¬î hairaga nakhoina makhoigi hakchanggi tangaiphadraba potchang adu pibidrabadi, madugi wadu hairubagi kanaba kari leibage?  
\v 17 Maduga chap manna thajabasuni, thabak yaodrabadi, madu asibani. 
\p  
\v 18 Adubu kanagumba mi amana haigani, ‚ÄúNanggidi thajaba lei aduga eigi thabak lei.‚Äù¬î Nahakki thajaba adu thabak yaodana eingonda utlu, aduga eigi thajaba adu eina nangonda eigi thabakna utke.  
\v 19 Tengban Mapu amakhak lei haiba asi nahakna thajei. Madu Aphabani! Lai phattabasingnasu madu thajei amasung kiduna thak thak nik-i.  
\v 20 He apangba mi, thabak yaodaba thajabadi kanadabani\f + \fr 2:20 \ft Ariba lairik kharada asiba haina yaoi\f* haiba nahakna khangningbra?  
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Khong 22:1-14\x* Eikhoigi ipa-ipu oiriba Abraham-bu achumba chatpa ama oina karamna singthanakhibage? Madu mahakki thabakki mapannani haibadi mahakna mahakki machanupa Isaac-pu latnapungda katkhiba matam adudani.  
\v 22 Nahak uba ngamdabra? Mahakki thajaba adu mahakki thabaksingga loinna chatminnei; mahakki thabakki mapanna mahakki thajaba adu mapung phahalli.  
\v 23 ‚ÄúAbraham-na Tengban Mapubu thajei, aduga madu mangonda achumba chatpa ama oina singthanabire,‚Äù¬î haiba Tengban Mapugi wahei adu thungle. Maram aduna mahakpu Tengban Mapugi marup haina koure.  
\v 24 Mi amabu mahakki touriba thabakki mapanna achumba chatpa ama oina singthanei madu thajaba ngaktana natte haiba nakhoina ure. 
\p  
\v 25 Matou adugumna oktabi Rahab-tasu oikhi. Mahakna toukhiba thabak adugi mapanna haibadi Israel-gi lanjabasing\f + \fr 2:25 \ft Yeknaba lanmigi ipao lonna loubasing\f* adu lousinbiba amadi makhoibu atoppa lambi amada nanthokpada mateng pangkhiba aduna mahakpu achumba chatpa oina singthanabikhi. 
\p  
\v 26 Maramdi thawai yaodraba hakchangna sibagum, thabak yaodaba thajaba adusu asibani. 
\c 3  
\s1 Lei khudum chanba 
\p  
\v 1 Eigi ichil-inaosa, nakhoi ayambana tambiba ojasing oiganu maramdi tambiba oja oiba eikhoi henna kanba wayenba phanggani haiba nakhoina khangliba aduni.  
\v 2 Eikhoi pumnamak toina asoiba toui. Adubu kanagumba mi amana mahakna haiba wada asoiba amata leitrabadi, mahak mapung phaba amasung mahakki masa apumba khudum chanba ngamba mi amani.  
\v 3 Eikhoigi haiba innanaba eikhoina sagolgi machinda yachan challi aduga eikhoina chatningba maphamda mahakpu chat-hanba ngammi.  
\v 4 Nattraga achouba hi\f + \fr 3:4 \ft Jahaj\f* amagi maramda wakhal tousi: hi adu yamna chaojarabasu amadi akanba nungsitna humlaga purabasu piklaba nougi mapanna hinao sabana\f + \fr 3:4 \ft Jahajbu mamai leiba mi\f* chatning chatningba maikeida koilei leiba ngammi.  
\v 5 Adugumduna lei asisuni: madu pikcharasu achou achoubasinggi maramda napan tou-i. Khanthabiyu, piklaba meirik amana chaokhraba umang amabu mei chak-hanba ngamlibani!  
\v 6 Leidi meigumbani, ayol arangi taibangpanbani; leina eikhoigi hakchang kayatsinggi marakta kayat ama oiduna hakchang apumbada phattaba sandok-i, amasung mahakki punsigi khongchat pumnamak norok-maktagi lakpa meina chak-halli.  
\v 7 Makhal khudingmakki sasing, ucheksing, mapukna sittuna chatpa sasing amasung isingda hinglibasingbu mioibana lakpa ngammi.  
\v 8 Adubu mi kana amatana leibu lakpadi ngamde. Masi khudum chanba ngamdaba phattaba amani, siba yaba huna thalli.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Meihou 1:26\x* Masigi lei asina eikhoina eikhoigi Mapu Ibungo amasung Ipabu thagatli, aduga Tengban Mapugi mitamda semkhraba misingbu eikhoina sirap tou-i.  
\v 10 Chin amatadagi thagat waheising amasung sirap touba thoklak-i. Eigi ichil inaosa, masi asumna oiroidabani!  
\v 11 Iphut amadagi thumhi chenba ising amasung thumhi chendaba ising animak thoklakte.  
\v 12 Eigi ichil inaosa, heiyit panbida chorphon panba yaba hounade aduga anggur pambida heiyit panba yaba hounade. Matou asumna thumhi chenba iphutna thumhi chendaba ising thok-hanba yaba hounade. 
\s1 Mathaklomdagi lakpa lousing 
\p  
\v 13 Nakhoigi narakta asingba amasung wakhal taba kanagumba yaobra? Mahakki aphaba punsi amadi lousing amasung nolukpaga loinna mahakna pangthokpa aphaba thabakna utsanu.  
\v 14 Adubu nakhoigi thamoinungda yamna kallakpa amasung masagi oijabata thiba adu karigumba leirabadi, nakhoina nakhoigi lousinggi maramda chaothoktuna achumbagi maiyokta pap langsin-ganu.  
\v 15 Adugumba lousing adudi swargadagi lakpa natte; madu taibangpangi oibani, thawaigi oiba natte lai phattabadagi oibani.  
\v 16 Kallakpa amasung masagi oijaba thiba leiba maphamda charangnaba amadi makhal khudingmakki phattaba adu lei.  
\v 17 Adubu swargadagi lakpa lousing adu ahanbada asengbani; adudagi ingthaba, pukning tappa, amasung marup mapang oiba; nungsiheibana thanba amasung aphaba thabakki maheising puthokpa; michang-mikhai naidaba amasung aphasasinnaba yaodaba oi.  
\v 18 Ingthabagi maru hunba ingthaba pibasingna achumba chatpagi mahei lok-i. 
\c 4  
\s1 Taibangpanbaga marup semba 
\p  
\v 1 Kadaidagi khatnaba amasung yetnaba nakhoigi narakta laklibano? Nakhoigi nungda leppa leitana lan soknariba ithak iranggi oiba nungaiba adugi apambasing adudagi lakpani.  
\v 2 Nakhoina karigumba khara pammi, adubu nakhoina madu phangba ngamde, maram aduna nakhoina hatnaba semsare; nakhoina karigumba khara yamna pamle adubu madu nakhoina phangba ngamdre, maram aduna nakhoi yetnare amadi khatnare. Nakhoina pamba adu nakhoina phangde maramdi nakhoina madugidamak Tengban Mapugi maphamda nijade.  
\v 3 Aduga nakhoina nijaba matamda, nakhoina madu phangde, maramdi nakhoina madu aranba pukninggi ithilga loinana nijei; nakhoigi nasagi nungaithokpagi apambasingda sijinnanaba oina nijei.  
\v 4 Thajaba yadaba mioisa! Taibangpanga marup oiba haibasi Tengban Mapuga yeknaba oibani haiba nakhoina khangdabra? Kanagumbana taibangpanga marup oininglabadi, mahak masana Tengban Mapuga yeknaba oihalle.  
\v 5 ‚ÄúTengban Mapuna eikhoigi nungda leihanbiba thawai aduna khourangna pammi‚Äù¬î\f + \fr 4:5 \ft Tengban Mapuna eikhoigi nungda pibiba thawai adubu Ibungona kalakchabaga loinana khourang-i\f* haiba Tengban Mapugi wahei asida achumba yaode khan-ganu.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Pao 3:34\x* Adubu Tengban Mapuna pibiba thoujal aduna henna kalli. Mapugi puyana asumna hai, ‚ÄúTengban Mapuna chaothokpasingbu thing-i, adubu nolukpasingda thoujal pinabi.‚Äù¬î 
\p  
\v 7 Maram aduna nakhoi nasamak Tengban Mapugi makha pollu. Devil-bu thing-u, aduga mahakna nangondagi chenkhigani.  
\v 8 Tengban Mapuda naksinjou, aduga mahakna nangonda naksinbirakkani. Papchenbasa, nakhoigi nakhut hamdok-u! Aphasasinnabasa, nakhoigi pukning sengdok-u!  
\v 9 Awaba pokpa oiyu, kappu amasung tengtha nawoioyu; nakhoigi nokpa adu kappada onthok-u, amasung nakhoigi haraoba adu awabada onthok-u!  
\v 10 Mapu Ibungogi mangda nakhoi nasamak nollukchou, aduga mahakna nakhoibu thanggatpigani. 
\s1 Amaga amaga wayennabagi mathakta cheksin wa haiba 
\p  
\v 11 Ichil inaosa, nakhoi amana amagi mathakta phattaba wa ngangnaganu. Nakhoi kanagumbana machin nanaogi mathakta thina ngangba nattraga wayenba mahak aduna Wayel Yathanggi mathakta thina ngangbani amadi Wayel Yathang adubu wayenbani, adunadi nahakna Wayel Yathang adubu ngakpa nattre, adubu madubu wayenbani.  
\v 12 Wayel yathang piba amasung wayenba adu Tengban Mapukhaktani. Mahaktana kanbiba amasung manghanba ngammi. Atoppa mibu wayelliba nahakpu kanani haina khanjaribano? 
\s1 Chaothokpasinggi mathakta piba cheksin wa 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13,14 \xt Pao 27:1\x* ‚ÄúNgasi nattraga hayeng eikhoina sahar aduda soidana chatlaga, eikhoina mapham aduda chahi ama leiraga lallon itik touduna sel mayam tan-gani‚Äù¬î hairiba nakhoi houjik eina hairiba asi tao.  
\v 14 Nakhoigi punsi hayeng kari oigani haiba phaoba nakhoina khangde! Nakhoidi mikup kharatamak leiramlaga mangkhiba manilgumbani.  
\v 15 Madugi mahutta nakhoina masi haigadabani: ‚ÄúMapu Ibungogi aningba oirabadi, eikhoi hinggani amasung masi nattraga madu tougani.‚Äù¬î  
\v 16 Adubu houjik nakhoi napal tou-i amasung chaothok-i; asigumna chaothokpa pumnamaksing asi aranbani. 
\p  
\v 17 Maram aduna kanagumbana makhoina tougadaba aphaba adu khanglaga toudrabadi, madu makhoigidamak papni. 
\c 5  
\s1 Inakkhunbasingda piba cheksin wa 
\p  
\v 1 He inakkhunbasa, houjik eina hairibasi tao! Nakhoigi nathakta lakkadaba awa ana adugidamak kappu amasung makhon thokna tengthao.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2,3\xt Mat 6:19\x* Nakhoigi lanthum patle, aduga nakhoigi phiron tinna chare.  
\v 3 Nakhoigi sana lupa kohling kare, aduga madugi kohling aduna nakhoigi maiyokta sakhi oigani amasung nakhoigi hakchangdu meigumna chakkani. Nakhoina akonba numitsinggidamak lanthum tungsinduna peisille.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Aniwa 24:14,15\x* Nakhoigi loubukta thabak subasing adugi khutsuman amata nakhoina pibidre. Nakhoigi maiyokta piriba makhoigi wakat asi tao! Nakhoigi lou khaobasinggi kappa adu Ingam ngamba Mapu Ibungogi nakong youkhre.  
\v 5 Nakhoina malemda kethok mouthokna amasung nasa nungaithokna lenthokle. Hatkadaba numit adugidamakta nakhoina nasamakpu thaktuna noihalle.  
\v 6 Nakhoigi maiyoktasu leitaba maral leitabasigbu nakhoina maral leihanduna hatli. 
\s1 Khaangheiba amasung haijaba 
\p  
\v 7 Maram aduna ichil inaosa, Mapu Ibungona lenglaktribaphaoba khaangheiba oiyu. Karamna loumisingna makhoigi lam aduna puthokkadaba mamal yamlaba mahei-marong adu ngaijabage haibadu yeng-u. Mahakna naken-tha amasung yening-thagi nonggidamak khaangheina ngaijei.  
\v 8 Nakhoisu khaangheiba oiyu amadi pukning chetna leppu maramdi Mapu Ibungona lenglakkadaba numit adu nakle. 
\p  
\v 9 Ichil inaosa, nakhoibu Tengban Mapuna wayendanaba, nakhoi amana amagi mathakta murum murum sonagagu. Wayen Mapu adu thongjinda leple.  
\v 10 Ichil inaosa, Mapu Ibungogi mingda wa ngangkhiba maichousingna awa anada khaangheiba oikhiba pandam adu loubiyu.  
\v 11 Awaba khaanglaba makhoi adubu eikhoina yaiphaba haina singthanei haibadu nakhoina khangliba aduni. Job-ki khaangheiba adu nakhoina tare aduga Mapu Ibungona mahakkidamak aroibada kari pibikhibage haiba nakhoina khangle. Mapu Ibungodi nungsiheiba amasung chanbiheibana thalli. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt Mat 5:34-37\x* Eigi ichil inaosa, pumnamak asidagi maruoiba adudi swarga nattraga malem, nattraga karigumba amatabu panduna wasakkanu. Nakhoina haigadaba adudi hoi oiragana ‚ÄúHoi‚Äù¬î haiyu nattraga mai oiragana ‚ÄúMai‚Äù¬î haiyu, madu oirabadi nakhoi Mapu Ibungogi wayenda taroi. 
\p  
\v 13 Nakhoigi narakta awaba nangba yaoribra? Makhoina haijasanu. Nakhoigi narakta kanagumba haraoba yaoribra? Makhoina thagat isei saksanu.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Mrk 6:13\x* Nakhoigi narakta anaba yaoribra? Makhoina singlupki ahallamansingbu kousanu, aduga makhoina Mapu Ibungogi mingda mahakpu thao teibiduna mahakkidamak haijabisanu.  
\v 15 Thajana haijaba aduna anaba mi adubu phahanbigani, aduga Mapu Ibungona makhoibu hanagi phibhamda amuk hanna phahanbigani. Karigumba makhoina pap langjaramlabadi, makhoigi pap adu kokpigani.  
\v 16 Maram aduna nakhoigi anaba phahanbinaba nakhoi amaga amaga pap haidoknaduna nakhoi amana amagidamak haijaminnou. Achumba chatpa migi haijabadi panggal kalli amasung thabak oina pangthok-i.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt 1 Ning 17:1; 18:1\x*Eikhoigumna Elijah-su mioiba amani. Nong chudanaba mahakna pukning changna haijakhi, adudagi leibak aduda chahi ahum makhai nong chukhide.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 5:18 \xt 1 Ning 18:42-45\x*Aduga mahakna amuk hanna haijare maduda atiyana nong chuhankhi amadi malemdagi mahei marong puthorakkhi. 
\p  
\v 19 Eigi ichil inaosa, nakhoigi naraktagi kanagumba amana achumbadagi lamuknakrabadi, atoppa amana mahakpu amuk hanna pubirakkadabani,  
\v 20 papchenba amabu mahakki aranba lambidagi pubirakpa mi aduna mahakki thawai adubu sibadagi kanbigani amasung pap mayam amabu kokpigani haiba asi ningsing-u.